      h3 睏/<ruby>困<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄨㄣˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>覺<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>
      dl
        dd [動]
        dd
